

     Contents of the ALICE: The Personal Pascal Distribution Disks:

PRIMARY ALICE DISK:		(*) means necessary to run ALICE

	ALICE.EXE	- The actual ALICE program (*)
	AP.INI		- ALICE configuration file, with startup options (*)
	APBUILT.SUF	- Built-in symbols and error messages (*)
	APTEMPLA.SUF	- Templates for the Pascal language (*)
	APIN.EXE	- Pascal parser that translates text versions of
			  Pascal programs into ALICE format
	TURBOLIB.AP	- Library of Turbo Pascal builtin routines
	SIEVE.AP	- Famous prime number program
	CONTENTS	- This file
	UPDATES		- Notes, bugs and errata for ALICE and manuals.
	TURBOLIB.PAS	- Source version of TURBOLIB.AP

ALICE SUPPLEMENTAL DISK:
	HELPFILE.HUF	- Compressed help files
	APRUN.BAT	- Standalone ALICE Pascal interpreter
	NLBEGIN.SUF	- Template file with alternate begin-end style
	SHOWEND.SUF	- Template file that shows block types on "end"s
	CPROC.DOC	- Documentation on C interface routines
	SYSPOINT.DOC	- Documentation on ALICE internal pointers
	QA.DOC		- Questions and Answers on ALICE
	APLIB		- Directory of ALICE libraries
		MENULIB.AP	- Pop-up menu routines
		ALICELIB.AP	- Alice interface routines
		CLIB.AP		- C style I/O interface
		MISCLIB.AP	- General C library routines
		APCOMMAND.AP	- Issue an ALICE command in a program
		WINDOW.AP	- CURSES windowing routines
		DOSLIB.AP	- IBM/DOS access
		DOSINT.AP	- DOS interface routines
		USEFUL.AP	- Chain and Execute routines

	SAMPLES		- Directory of sample programs
		( Some require a machine with >256K to run)
		PLOT.AP		- Sample character plot program.
		COLOURS.AP	- Change text attributes
		MACROLIS.AP	- List defined macros
		SECRET.AP	- Guess a secret code game.
		STARSHIP.AP	- Real time Starship Pilot game.
		CMAN.AP		- Colour 'Mandala' Graphics demo
		BOUNCE.AP	- Bouncing Ball program for ALICE
		BALLS.IM	- Data for BOUNCE.AP
		INV.AP		- Inventory program
		INV.DOC		- Documentation for Inventory program
	TURBO		- Directory of Turbo Pascal related files.
		ALICELIB.TP	- Turbo Pascal versions of Alice builtins
		GRAPH.P		- Turbo Pascal Turtle/Extended Graphics
				  include file.  (Requires GRAPH.BIN)
		PORT		- Notes on portablility.

	SORTS		- Directory of simple sorting programs.
			  It can be instructional to run these with
			  "Cursor Following On."
		BUBBLE.AP,HEAP.AP,INSERTIO.AP,MERGE.AP,QUICK.AP,
		RADIX.AP,SELECTIO.AP,SHELL.AP,STUPID.AP
